Version 1.1
 - Add showing vendor of network interface. The vendor is defined by
   means of prefixes of mac addresses.
 - Import from custom file mapping mac addresses into ip addresses and
   host names.
 - Add restriction of local network interfaces for arp scanning.
 - Execution of all external command is logged now.
 - Fix bug of incorrect mapping local ip addresses.

Version 1.0
 - First public release.
